CP applications\n1:34 Looking back at the evolution of the MCP ecosystem over the last 18 months\n2:30 Ecosystem growth and adoption milestones\n3:46 Moving from exploration in 2025 to production in 2026\n5:07 The 2026 connectivity stack: Skills, MCP, and CLI/Computer use\n7:47 Improving client harnesses: Progressive Discovery\n9:39 Programmatic tool calling and agent orchestration\n12:00 Best practices for designing agents and server authors\n13:42 Future roadmap for the MCP protocol and core improvements\n15:23 Strategic integrations and enterprise features\n16:32 Upcoming extension mechanisms and skills over MCP\n17:15 Conclusion and call for community feedback","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":192,"length":18,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"COICEM2rARgBIhMIi-nLs63_kwMVxUI4BR0HrRhfSKDZ46OJ-9q4vwHKAQTr2442","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0J5VlREVXlQeVNFMnR2STB5UkRPZm5Hc3Bsd3xBQ3Jtc0tsLU5HQm91cFE0MkFXSzJsa3BHWmQ0SHc1YkFpLUh6ay0yOUM1Rm5XcDBOMWlqWVRSc1B4MUxORGdtb21aVkg5U1pTRHZqMmVzOFJleWxPNGVmT2hWN0RYdFR5YUI2SVN3algzXzlvY3pnb01QLUFyOA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdsp_\u0026v=v3Fr2JR47KA","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0J5VlREVXlQeVNFMnR2STB5UkRPZm5Hc3Bsd3xBQ3Jtc0tsLU5HQm91cFE0MkFXSzJsa3BHWmQ0SHc1YkFpLUh6ay0yOUM1Rm5XcDBOMWlqWVRSc1B4MUxORGdtb21aVkg5U1pTRHZqMmVzOFJleWxPNGVmT2hWN0RYdFR5YUI2SVN3algzXzlvY3pnb01QLUFyOA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdsp_\u0026v=v3Fr2JR47KA","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":211,"length":31,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"COICEM2rARgBIhMIi-nLs63_kwMVxUI4BR0HrRhfSKDZ46OJ-9q4vwHKAQTr2442","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDkzcG9kekc4RVlKaEl1TWNxaWxLZHFid2xKZ3xBQ